    "intro": "Application is where Observation and Interpretation become obedience. Each question is tied to a specific movement of the chapter — read it slowly, answer it honestly, and name a specific situation in your life. Jeremiah 49 does not address believers directly; it addresses nations through the prophetic word. The application therefore asks: where does this nation's sin live in my own heart?",
